{"text_id":127177,"tokens":["Motiv","ated"," by"," the"," prevalence"," of"," monotonic"," and"," fast","-","deca","ying"," monotonic"," distributions"," in"," various"," applications"," ranging"," from"," machine"," learning"," to"," signal"," processing",","," we"," investigate"," universal"," source"," coding"," techniques"," for"," these"," distributions","."," We"," develop"," a"," novel"," entropy","-","based"," coding"," scheme"," that"," lever","ages"," the"," inherent"," structure"," of"," these"," distributions"," to"," achieve"," near","-","optimal"," compression"," rates","."," Our"," approach"," utilizes"," a"," combination"," of","  ","coarse","-","grained"," quantization"," and"," fine","-","grained"," entropy"," coding",","," effectively"," exploiting"," the"," spars","ity"," and"," predictability"," of"," the"," data","."," We"," establish"," theoretical"," bounds"," on"," the"," achievable"," distortion"," for"," both"," monotonic"," and"," fast","-","deca","ying"," monotonic"," distributions","."," Notably",","," our"," results"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," proposed"," scheme"," significantly"," out","performs"," conventional"," universal"," cod","ers",","," achieving"," compression"," gains","  ","close"," to"," those"," achievable"," by"," distribution","-","specific"," cod","ers"," while"," maintaining"," the"," desirable"," property"," of"," universality",".","  ","These"," findings"," contribute"," to"," the"," advancement"," of"," universal"," source"," coding"," theory"," and"," provide"," a"," practical"," tool"," for"," efficiently"," comp","ressing"," data"," arising"," from"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," real","-","world"," scenarios","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma2-9b-it","label":1}